{"id":547245,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2016/12/文三娃：江西乐平案被告改判无罪-多少律师如鲠在/","date":"2016-12-23T05:35:22Z","modified":"2016-12-23T08:03:36Z","title":"文三娃：江西乐平案被告改判无罪 多少律师如鲠在喉","content":"<blockquote><p><strong>相关阅读</strong>：<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2016/12/%e5%87%a4%e5%87%b0%e7%bd%91%ef%bd%9c%e5%af%b9%e8%af%9d%e4%b9%90%e5%b9%b3%e6%a1%88%e5%be%8b%e5%b8%88%ef%bc%9a%e4%bb%8a%e5%90%8e%e5%86%a4%e6%a1%88%e5%b9%b3%e5%8f%8d%e8%b6%8a%e5%8f%91%e5%80%9a%e9%87%8d/\" target=\"_blank\">凤凰网｜对话乐平案律师：今后冤案平反越发倚重当事人运气 </a></p></blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"http://weibo.com/u/5933520487\" target=\"_blank\">@三娃的厨房</a>：江西乐平案再审，服刑14年的四名被告改判无罪。律界于此案庭里庭外的抗争，绵长而惨烈。为蒙冤当事人抱火者，相继身陷囹圄。被告人及其辩护人终于迎来这场惨胜时，身心俱疲。法治之光影影绰绰，多少律师如鲠在喉，其鸣也哀。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/12/006tyrJljw1fazgfwvd2jj30qo0zkwgx.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-547247\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/12/006tyrJljw1fazgfwvd2jj30qo0zkwgx.jpg\" alt=\"006tyrjljw1fazgfwvd2jj30qo0zkwgx\" width=\"525\" height=\"700\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/12/006tyrJljw1fazgfwvd2jj30qo0zkwgx.jpg 960w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/12/006tyrJljw1fazgfwvd2jj30qo0zkwgx-225x300.jpg 225w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/12/006tyrJljw1fazgfwvd2jj30qo0zkwgx-768x1024.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 525px) 100vw, 525px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/12/006tyrJljw1fazgfx8xmtj30qo0zkmzm.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-547248\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/12/006tyrJljw1fazgfx8xmtj30qo0zkmzm.jpg\" alt=\"006tyrjljw1fazgfx8xmtj30qo0zkmzm\" width=\"525\" height=\"700\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/12/006tyrJljw1fazgfx8xmtj30qo0zkmzm.jpg 960w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/12/006tyrJljw1fazgfx8xmtj30qo0zkmzm-225x300.jpg 225w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2016/12/006ty